== Kinki Region ==
* {{ill|Koyasu Shrine (Ise)|ja|子安神社 (伊勢市)}} - Located in Ise City, Mie Prefecture, under the jurisdiction of the {{ill|Inner Shrine|ja|皇大神宮}}.
* {{ill|Koyasu Shrine (Kihoku)|ja|子安神社 (紀宝町)}} - Located in Jinai, Kiho Town, Minami-Muro District, Mie Prefecture.

== Chugoku Region ==
* {{ill|Koyasu Shrine (Okayama)|ja|子安神社 (岡山市)}} - Located in Kita Ward, Okayama City, Okayama Prefecture. A subordinate shrine of {{ill|Kibitsu Shrine|ja|吉備津彦神社}}.

