==Access==
* By bus: From the south exit of {{ill|Iseshi Station|en|Iseshi Station|qid=Q6079748|lt=Ise Station|1=Iseshi Station}} (JR Sangu Line) or {{ill|Ujiyamada Station|en|Ujiyamada Station|qid=Q7878210|lt=Ujiyamada Station|1=Ujiyamada Station}} (Kintetsu Yamada/Toba Line), take the Mie Kotsu bus to Naikū-mae (Inner Shrine entrance), approx. 15 minutes<ref name="mkr">三重県観光連盟 “[http://www.kankomie.or.jp/spot/detail_2937.html 伊勢神宮（内宮）の観光施設・周辺情報 - 観光三重]” (accessed September 12 2013)</ref>. Buses also run from {{ill|Isuzugawa Station|en|Isuzugawa Station|qid=Q6089533|lt=Isuzugawa Station|1=Isuzugawa Station}} on the Toba Line.
